'From Squeak3.4gamma of ''7 January 2003'' [latest update: #5169] on 19 February 2003 at 4:11:55 pm'!"Change Set:		DictionaryCommentFix-dtlDate:			19 February 2003Author:			David T. LewisFixed the method comment for Dictionary>>valuesDo:Comment was:  Evaluate aBlock for each of the receiver's keys.Changed to:  Evaluate aBlock for each of the receiver's values."!!Dictionary methodsFor: 'enumerating' stamp: 'dtl 2/17/2003 09:48'!valuesDo: aBlock 	"Evaluate aBlock for each of the receiver's values."	self associationsDo: [:association | aBlock value: association value]! !